their boss . because of all of the advantages running an authoritarian business has in the government and law , even people wanting to create a more democratic business have very little leeway to do freedoms and it hinders the spread of liberty . i also appreciate many of the similarities between right and left wing libertarians and i think we have more in common than most would have us believe . free , and by including more options and removing many of the state capitalist barriers that the government props up , we can have a more free society . we can argue over the right to health and education after we have together reduced much of the undue power state capitalism has achieved .
